-11-02T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"多數呢啲非公營機構/政府醫院申請禁制令都唔會開緊急庭，等番一兩年就有得審<br />\n到時一係立左國一係全民皆藍了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:30:06.000Z","msg":"議員應該會好快審??"},{"pid":"bcff6ee90bd391a223d5a8bb2dc9143bdce9eb4c","tid":1689222,"uid":266388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abc828cb513e00546f780fa8676987758fc62d93","tid":1689222,"uid":81385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"多數呢啲非公營機構/政府醫院申請禁制令都唔會開緊急庭，等番一兩年就有得審<br />\n到時一係立左國一係全民皆藍了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8d6432ca1dfabc5174a24bf433c3a8dfffb261","tid":1689222,"uid":286753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10c62413b6e07c2beb5c3e6af436eab14136b487","tid":1689222,"uid":336462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:31:22.000Z","msg":"你願意為被捕人士同失去眼睛和生命的手足爭取公義嗎！<br />\n你又願意為公義冒險ma !<br />\n<br />\n@vvovv2019"},{"pid":"67881619fd77f7fae2181f9eca3c9f15bbf5a673","tid":1689222,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:36:10.000Z","msg":"TUI"},{"pid":"1303c9e0e27b404a5844ce9288f09705a9a4b6be","tid":1689222,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:45:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e6be6a42dacd93c0d1d61f9a5e7995ca718b1250","tid":1689222,"uid":244087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:49:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d12382d2207d7e13d70df156f9eed100c568079c","tid":1689222,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:52:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5a480ac1438541a5ff00b5569433ae93ed4f0586","tid":1689222,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:52:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1311468850f26b046a2558aa007243949ef75023","tid":1689222,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0